title: pytorch vs LuaJIT torch
body_html:
It's unsettling that there is no explanation in the blog post, documentation or here of the real relationship between both projects.

I think it would be very useful to explain that relationship and maybe foster other projects. I'd love to see a gotorch equivalent, if that made sense!
